<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA3">
<l>maṉattuḷḷāṉ mākaṭaṉī ruḷḷāṉ malarā</l>
<l>ṭaṉattuḷḷāṉ ṟaṇṭuḻāy mārpaṉ – ciṉattuc</l>
<l>cerunarukac ceṟṟukanta tēṅkōta vaṇṇaṉ</l>
<l>varunarakan tīrkku maruntu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He is in [my] mind; he is on the water of the great sea; he belongs</l>
<l>to her of the blossom; he with cool tulsi on [his] chest, he the colour</l>
<l>of the rising flood who rejoices in subduing the enemies so that they fall</l> 
<l>in [their] anger, [he is] the remedy that ends coming hells.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
